OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FLargely cloudy and dry at
OL,6,Ffirst, but a few showers are possible
OL,7,Fthis afternoon as the cloud thickens.
OL,8,FPerhaps a few brighter breaks across
OL,9,FCumbria to end the day.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FShowers will clear to the
OL,12,Fsouth, followed by a dry night with
OL,13,Fclear spells. Turning chilly where the
OL,14,Fskies clear.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FLargely dry and cloudy on
OL,17,FTuesday, although a few showers are
OL,18,Fpossible in the afternoon. Feeling
OL,19,Fcool under the cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
